{"tid":1279717,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"網路戰實戰攻略","createTime":"2019-07-02T17:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T17:44:10.000Z","uid":159956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bea5f468caeace194c5a6b8354a72b9d98001bb2","tid":1279717,"uid":159956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:44:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家好，小弟第一次係呢度出post。小弟希望可以用自己嘅小小經驗為香港一盡綿力，小弟正職同點樣正確使用Facebook非常有關，所以都想係度分享下網路世界都可以做多啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n講講依家其實Facebook係點樣運作，Facebook作為一個網路社區+商家賣廣告之地，佢地營運標準好簡單，就係要留住你睇！所以好簡單，佢只係會派你想睇嘅野比你睇。乜野係你想睇嘅野？就係你平時你會like comment share嘅野。<br />\n<br />\n講到呢個位，我認為Facebook呢個網路重地我地有野可以做，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><strong>簡單嚟講分兩大類，一就係撐自己人，二就係打狗打鬼打共媒。<br />\n<br />\n先講撐自己人。Facebook可以岀post嘅account有兩種，personal同page。兩種page嘅post嘅行動大同小異，大家下面可以參考下：<br />\n<br />\n1) 記得比反應，簡單嘅like又好haha又好心心又好，唔洗諗㩒咗先，唔好慳喇風頭火勢，比個like唔會少忽肉<br />\n2)有野想討論，就留幾隻字 / 有戰友頂唔順，都不妨同佢地學術交流下 / 為戰友打打氣，一舉兩得<br />\n3)覺得講嘅野有point應該比更多人知，記得記得記得share，比更多朋友戰友睇。<br />\n4Page第一樣係要like，重要嘅page好似立場呢啲，最好㩒埋see first （手足有啲咩page好麻煩都幫幫手係度list出嚟）<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MA4LQzw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMA4LQzw.png&h=e0c8c9a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gachGGc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgachGGc.png&h=3f7c863e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8FE4mGd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8FE4mGd.png&h=57fc1f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就到點處理講起都嬲嘅廢老最愛&mdash;共媒共page （都請手足幫手list out下等大家一齊做野），都係一樣野 report report 同埋都係 report。<br />\n1）Report post&mdash;一來可以睇下佢地講咩野睇下佢地有咩野高見，睇完就梗係幫佢地一個大忙，等佢地嘅野唔好再留係度影響大家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38htOmO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38htOmO.png&h=f06b32f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REzDq8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREzDq8v.png&h=005586cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2）Report account&mdash;啲廢老共匪咁鐘意講多野，又覺得自己咁行得正企得正，咁不如唔洗影分身啦，用番真身嚟當面對質，report曬佢地啲影分身等Facebook block曬啲假account，我地就可以同佢地we connect好好對話啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tq3wL8J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTq3wL8J.png&h=6c7aa504&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fNPG8m4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfNPG8m4.png&h=0fd04a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3）Report page&mdash;冇平台，就冇地方比佢地亂做假新聞假消息，搞我地自己人，所以report page係非常非常非常重要，做完上面兩步，千奇唔好漏呢步</strong></strong></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/St5jaA1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSt5jaA1.png&h=895ee0d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/03/005945_d41d606c4c5c1713b5ce9ed824dd1db9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F03%2F005945_d41d606c4c5c1713b5ce9ed824dd1db9.png&h=dab5e679&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BRcahgs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBRcahgs.png&h=f759c43a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NhKLQBt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNhKLQBt.png&h=e5fad6cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XaYTZuR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXaYTZuR.png&h=85a0c02d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phA7juS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FphA7juS.png&h=9b7345b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家肯花時間睇曬，手足們有咩野高見都可妨留低一齊相討下，小弟諗到其他都拿再向大家講。<br />\n<br />\n#不撤不散<br />\n#釋放義士<br />\n#一個都不能少<br />\n#多你一個就多好多<br />\n#香港加油<br />\n</span>"}]}